messages.message:
@Aayush converse-app seems to still be a frequent perpetrator. It would be easier if it were failing with the same error each time but it always seems to be different. Here are four examples:
https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10138/overview/5ae8b053-70b8-48b7-a273-9b484068b2d5?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10137/overview/5b5b95f1-519f-4724-b2f3-bcf1c98f1a22?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10122/overview/560fb3a6-6fdf-4545-8eae-2fa253d68263?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
https://cloud.cypress.io/projects/cfhedy/runs/10112/overview/9a7e82a5-ece4-4a27-8380-11940e407585?roarHideRunsWithDiffGroupsAndTags=1
In two of those, it's actually the only error out of 127 tests - so if we can fix this one it will have an outsized impact

Created this PR to make it safe to run parallely: https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/57698

Hopefully it resolves most of the above issues
